{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-009__001__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 1, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·009.1", "text_original": "孑孑干旄，在浚之郊，素絲紕之，良馬四之，彼姝者子，何以畀之。", "text_normalized": "孑孑干旄，在浚之郊，素絲紕之，良馬四之，彼姝者子，何以畀之。", "notes": "干旄 Chinese stanza 1."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-009__002__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 2, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·009.2", "text_original": "孑孑干旟，在浚之都，素絲組之，良馬五之，彼姝者子，何以予之。", "text_normalized": "孑孑干旟，在浚之都，素絲組之，良馬五之，彼姝者子，何以予之。", "notes": "干旄 Chinese stanza 2."}
{"segment_id": "shijing__guofeng-yongfeng-009__003__zhwikisource-20260530", "work_id": "shijing", "section_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-009", "source_id": "guofeng-yongfeng-009__zhwikisource-20260530", "segment_type": "stanza", "segment_order": 3, "canonical_ref": "詩經·國風·鄘風·009.3", "text_original": "孑孑干旌，在浚之城，素絲祝之，良馬六之，彼姝者子，何以告之。", "text_normalized": "孑孑干旌，在浚之城，素絲祝之，良馬六之，彼姝者子，何以告之。", "notes": "干旄 Chinese stanza 3."}
